post_body: If I had gotten a tattoo when I was seven…. Second project for the Find your Style course.   I had to come up with a tattoo I would have been down to have as a 6 or 7 year old that was based around life experiences. I loved playing tag like in a big way. I went to school because it meant on lunch it was tag time. And it was one of the only reasons I actually went to school willingly.   Going through the first part of this course was pretty big for me. It showed me the things that made the greatest impact on me as a person and as an artist. Not surprisingly cinema played a big part of that the characters I saw on screen impacted what I thought was cool and the kind of art I liked to create.   ALT   It showed me the pattern over years of growth as an artist how I went from generating sad very dark work to trying to generate healing through art by creating art that was fun whimsical and care-free.   Procreate has lent to my style in a big way taking things from a sketch to a final digital piece that still emulates the nature of pastel on paper or ink on card stock. It’s imperfect yet lovely. Just like me.

post_body: If I had gotten a tattoo when I was seven…. Second project for the Find your Style course.   I had to come up with a tattoo I would have been down to have as a 6 or 7 year old that was based around life experiences. I loved playing tag like in a big way. I went to school because it meant on lunch it was tag time. And it was one of the only reasons I actually went to school willingly.   Going through the first part of this course was pretty big for me. It showed me the things that made the greatest impact on me as a person and as an artist. Not surprisingly cinema played a big part of that the characters I saw on screen impacted what I thought was cool and the kind of art I liked to create.   ALT   It showed me the pattern over years of growth as an artist how I went from generating sad very dark work to trying to generate healing through art by creating art that was fun whimsical and care-free.   Procreate has lent to my style in a big way taking things from a sketch to a final digital piece that still emulates the nature of pastel on paper or ink on card stock. It’s imperfect yet lovely. Just like me.

post_body: If I had gotten a tattoo when I was seven…. Second project for the Find your Style course.   I had to come up with a tattoo I would have been down to have as a 6 or 7 year old that was based around life experiences. I loved playing tag like in a big way. I went to school because it meant on lunch it was tag time. And it was one of the only reasons I actually went to school willingly.   Going through the first part of this course was pretty big for me. It showed me the things that made the greatest impact on me as a person and as an artist. Not surprisingly cinema played a big part of that the characters I saw on screen impacted what I thought was cool and the kind of art I liked to create.   ALT   It showed me the pattern over years of growth as an artist how I went from generating sad very dark work to trying to generate healing through art by creating art that was fun whimsical and care-free.   Procreate has lent to my style in a big way taking things from a sketch to a final digital piece that still emulates the nature of pastel on paper or ink on card stock. It’s imperfect yet lovely. Just like me.

post_body: If I had gotten a tattoo when I was seven…. Second project for the Find your Style course.   I had to come up with a tattoo I would have been down to have as a 6 or 7 year old that was based around life experiences. I loved playing tag like in a big way. I went to school because it meant on lunch it was tag time. And it was one of the only reasons I actually went to school willingly.   Going through the first part of this course was pretty big for me. It showed me the things that made the greatest impact on me as a person and as an artist. Not surprisingly cinema played a big part of that the characters I saw on screen impacted what I thought was cool and the kind of art I liked to create.   ALT   It showed me the pattern over years of growth as an artist how I went from generating sad very dark work to trying to generate healing through art by creating art that was fun whimsical and care-free.   Procreate has lent to my style in a big way taking things from a sketch to a final digital piece that still emulates the nature of pastel on paper or ink on card stock. It’s imperfect yet lovely. Just like me.

post_body: SNOW SEACLAW IN HER QUEEN DRESS I looked at lot of middle ages stuff to get a inspiration. Nothing really specific lol but I did give her a super cool scepter muahaha. She also got cool flower shapes! I love her and her design I understand why you guys voted her for fan favourite in my Bevel and Snow post  Btw I fixed her ocelli (Three simple eyes arranged in an upside down triangle on insects) because they’re meant to be an upside down triangle sorry my mistake…. BUT THE THING IS MY LAST BRAINCELL WORKING OVERTIME FORGOT ABOUT THEM IN THE SNOW REFERENCE!!! UGHHHHHHHHHHHHHH  I am really happy because the bloodshed has ended no more period for me yayyyyyyyy!! Doomsday is gone!!  Here’s Bevel too. I gave her those kinda of trousers that are puffy. Though I don’t really like this drawing at least it will prove a great reference for her attires! Btw she smells like flowers and wood and probably a lot of Wasp pheromones. So imagine a woody flower scent fighting with musk… maybe pheromones smell different to other Wasps and then that smell will like cling to them. That sounds like a good idea it may not be very accurate but hey! Oh yeah and probably alcohol she drinks alcohol time to time. That was such a weird paragraph… you probably don’t want to know what Bevel smells like… well don’t worry Snow just smells like fruit honey and flowers!!!  Please get Bevel more perfume  Don’t judge but BEVEL IS A TALL ASS WASP. SNOW IS MEANT TO BE THE LARGEST WASP BECAUSE SHE’S QUEEN BUT NO! BEVEL JUST HAD TO BE TALLER. Justice for Snow. They look so interesting when you put them beside eachother. Bevel is like tall I didn’t measure her  Should we rehost the poll? I think we should!  Who is the favourite?  Snow  Bevel  Both  See Results Snow won last time btw! I HOPE THIS WAS AN EFFICIENT FOOD FOR YOU EAT UP MY CHILDREN!  That was fun goodbye! (Will Wood reference)

Btw she smells like flowers and wood and probably a lot of Wasp pheromones. So imagine a woody flower scent fighting with musk… maybe pheromones smell different to other Wasps and then that smell will like cling to them. That sounds like a good idea it may not be very accurate but hey! Oh yeah and probably alcohol she drinks alcohol time to time. That was such a weird paragraph… you probably don’t want to know what Bevel smells like… well don’t worry Snow just smells like fruit honey and flowers!!! I love her and her design I understand why you guys voted her for fan favourite in my Bevel and Snow post  Btw I fixed her ocelli (Three simple eyes arranged in an upside down triangle on insects) because they’re meant to be an upside down triangle sorry my mistake…. BUT THE THING IS MY LAST BRAINCELL WORKING OVERTIME FORGOT ABOUT THEM IN THE SNOW REFERENCE!!! UGHHHHHHHHHHHHHH  I am really happy because the bloodshed has ended no more period for me yayyyyyyyy!! Doomsday is gone!!  Here’s Bevel too. I gave her those kinda of trousers that are puffy. Though I don’t really like this drawing at least it will prove a great reference for her attires! Btw she smells like flowers and wood and probably a lot of Wasp pheromones. So imagine a woody flower scent fighting with musk… maybe pheromones smell different to other Wasps and then that smell will like cling to them. That sounds like a good idea it may not be very accurate but hey! Oh yeah and probably alcohol she drinks alcohol time to time. That was such a weird paragraph… you probably don’t want to know what Bevel smells like… well don’t worry Snow just smells like fruit honey and flowers!!!  Please get Bevel more perfume  Don’t judge but BEVEL IS A TALL ASS WASP. SNOW IS MEANT TO BE THE LARGEST WASP BECAUSE SHE’S QUEEN BUT NO! BEVEL JUST HAD TO BE TALLER. Justice for Snow. They look so interesting when you put them beside eachother. Bevel is like tall I didn’t measure her  Should we rehost the poll? I think we should!  Who is the favourite?  Snow  Bevel  Both  See Results Snow won last time btw! I HOPE THIS WAS AN EFFICIENT FOOD FOR YOU EAT UP MY CHILDREN!  That was fun goodbye! (Will Wood reference)

Btw she smells like flowers and wood and probably a lot of Wasp pheromones. That sounds like a good idea it may not be very accurate but hey! Oh yeah and probably alcohol she drinks alcohol time to time. That was such a weird paragraph… you probably don’t want to know what Bevel smells like… well don’t worry Snow just smells like fruit honey and flowers!!!  Please get Bevel more perfume  Don’t judge but BEVEL IS A TALL ASS WASP. SNOW IS MEANT TO BE THE LARGEST WASP BECAUSE SHE’S QUEEN BUT NO! BEVEL JUST HAD TO BE TALLER. Justice for Snow. KO-FI and Paypal links Ko-fi is set up weird so I prefer paypal after directly talking to me in DMs   Unavailable atm unless you want to have a christmas pfp for $5  If you can’t buy PLEASE reblog this post.

For a rewrite of what’s on there   Tos (terms of service) - Prices are paid beforehand (fyi YES you will get a refund if something comes up.) - No choosing beggars (aka no bartering with like ‘well can it be-’ no it’s what I set it as.) - No NSFW - No robots (I’m not advanced enough in robots and I want to make something worth your money) - No Hazbin/Helluva - Please be patient. I’m spending time making you something and that obviously takes literal time. I’m not a machine.   Prices:   Cleaned sketch - $5 Lineart - $10 Flats - $15 Rendered: $20 (Unavailable) Bg (On any) - additional $5   FYI I will fix small mistakes for you if its a minor error.   I feel like these are high prices but also I don’t want to undersell myself like so many artists warn new commission artists about. So I think starting at 5 and ending at 20-25 is okay and fair.   KO-FI and Paypal links Ko-fi is set up weird so I prefer paypal after directly talking to me in DMs   Unavailable atm unless you want to have a christmas pfp for $5  If you can’t buy PLEASE reblog this post.

For a rewrite of what’s on there   Tos (terms of service) - Prices are paid beforehand (fyi YES you will get a refund if something comes up.) - No choosing beggars (aka no bartering with like ‘well can it be-’ no it’s what I set it as.) - No NSFW - No robots (I’m not advanced enough in robots and I want to make something worth your money) - No Hazbin/Helluva - Please be patient. Prices:   Cleaned sketch - $5 Lineart - $10 Flats - $15 Rendered: $20 (Unavailable) Bg (On any) - additional $5   FYI I will fix small mistakes for you if its a minor error.   I feel like these are high prices but also I don’t want to undersell myself like so many artists warn new commission artists about. So I think starting at 5 and ending at 20-25 is okay and fair.   KO-FI and Paypal links Ko-fi is set up weird so I prefer paypal after directly talking to me in DMs   Unavailable atm unless you want to have a christmas pfp for $5  If you can’t buy PLEASE reblog this post.

She also got cool flower shapes! BUT THE THING IS MY LAST BRAINCELL WORKING OVERTIME FORGOT ABOUT THEM IN THE SNOW REFERENCE!!! UGHHHHHHHHHHHHHH  I am really happy because the bloodshed has ended no more period for me yayyyyyyyy!! Btw she smells like flowers and wood and probably a lot of Wasp pheromones. So imagine a woody flower scent fighting with musk… maybe pheromones smell different to other Wasps and then that smell will like cling to them. That sounds like a good idea it may not be very accurate but hey! Oh yeah and probably alcohol she drinks alcohol time to time. That was such a weird paragraph… you probably don’t want to know what Bevel smells like… well don’t worry Snow just smells like fruit honey and flowers!!!  Please get Bevel more perfume  Don’t judge but BEVEL IS A TALL ASS WASP. SNOW IS MEANT TO BE THE LARGEST WASP BECAUSE SHE’S QUEEN BUT NO! BEVEL JUST HAD TO BE TALLER. Justice for Snow. post_body: Commissions  This is a terrible ref sheet but over time I’ll get the hang of it.   For a rewrite of what’s on there   Tos (terms of service) - Prices are paid beforehand (fyi YES you will get a refund if something comes up.) - No choosing beggars (aka no bartering with like ‘well can it be-’ no it’s what I set it as.) - No NSFW - No robots (I’m not advanced enough in robots and I want to make something worth your money) - No Hazbin/Helluva - Please be patient. I’m spending time making you something and that obviously takes literal time. I’m not a machine.   Prices:   Cleaned sketch - $5 Lineart - $10 Flats - $15 Rendered: $20 (Unavailable) Bg (On any) - additional $5   FYI I will fix small mistakes for you if its a minor error.   I feel like these are high prices but also I don’t want to undersell myself like so many artists warn new commission artists about. So I think starting at 5 and ending at 20-25 is okay and fair.   KO-FI and Paypal links Ko-fi is set up weird so I prefer paypal after directly talking to me in DMs   Unavailable atm unless you want to have a christmas pfp for $5  If you can’t buy PLEASE reblog this post.

post_body: Commissions  This is a terrible ref sheet but over time I’ll get the hang of it.   For a rewrite of what’s on there   Tos (terms of service) - Prices are paid beforehand (fyi YES you will get a refund if something comes up.) - No choosing beggars (aka no bartering with like ‘well can it be-’ no it’s what I set it as.) - No NSFW - No robots (I’m not advanced enough in robots and I want to make something worth your money) - No Hazbin/Helluva - Please be patient. I’m spending time making you something and that obviously takes literal time. I’m not a machine.   Prices:   Cleaned sketch - $5 Lineart - $10 Flats - $15 Rendered: $20 (Unavailable) Bg (On any) - additional $5   FYI I will fix small mistakes for you if its a minor error.   I feel like these are high prices but also I don’t want to undersell myself like so many artists warn new commission artists about. So I think starting at 5 and ending at 20-25 is okay and fair.   KO-FI and Paypal links Ko-fi is set up weird so I prefer paypal after directly talking to me in DMs   Unavailable atm unless you want to have a christmas pfp for $5  If you can’t buy PLEASE reblog this post.

post_body: BEE TIME!!! This (I think) a type of Valley Carpenter bee that’s all gold and yellow!  He chonk and fluff! Do not judge  This is a Green Sweat Bee unless it has a more specific name.  I had a hard time with this one trying to get the right greens and bluish green lol  I don’t know if this is a she or he yet.  Not the last sketch! But I thought Horn faced bees were silly. They’re a type of Mason Bee if I’m correct  If you haven’t figured it out these are solitary Bees!  He looks like someone who eats ice cream a ton (Specifically chocolate or uhhh… Neapolitan I only ate the chocolate part of those giant tubs I had from Walmart…)  SHE SWORE SHE WOULD’NT EAT THEM. Beewolf Wasps were just so awesome to me and I HAD to draw them or I would die  Beewolf Wasps are solitary btw that means no hive no queen no friends either. I’m just kidding they have friends no MORTAL ENEMIES.  I did rip sketches from my sketchbook to draw and fix and stuff  Here’s two ant doodles. I AN ARTIST HOLD THE POWER TO DO… Idk something? I’m honestly trying to get better at expressions  Love you guys! Also I genuinely listen to That Handsome Devil he is starving his fans of new music :( FEED ME SEYMOUR!!! (Little Shop of Horrors ref)  Okay no actually farewell

I’m just kidding they have friends no MORTAL ENEMIES.  I did rip sketches from my sketchbook to draw and fix and stuff  Here’s two ant doodles. I AN ARTIST HOLD THE POWER TO DO… Idk something? post_body: BEE TIME!!! This (I think) a type of Valley Carpenter bee that’s all gold and yellow!  He chonk and fluff! Do not judge  This is a Green Sweat Bee unless it has a more specific name.  I had a hard time with this one trying to get the right greens and bluish green lol  I don’t know if this is a she or he yet.  Not the last sketch! But I thought Horn faced bees were silly. They’re a type of Mason Bee if I’m correct  If you haven’t figured it out these are solitary Bees!  He looks like someone who eats ice cream a ton (Specifically chocolate or uhhh… Neapolitan I only ate the chocolate part of those giant tubs I had from Walmart…)  SHE SWORE SHE WOULD’NT EAT THEM. Beewolf Wasps were just so awesome to me and I HAD to draw them or I would die  Beewolf Wasps are solitary btw that means no hive no queen no friends either. I’m just kidding they have friends no MORTAL ENEMIES.  I did rip sketches from my sketchbook to draw and fix and stuff  Here’s two ant doodles. I AN ARTIST HOLD THE POWER TO DO… Idk something? I’m honestly trying to get better at expressions  Love you guys! Also I genuinely listen to That Handsome Devil he is starving his fans of new music :( FEED ME SEYMOUR!!!
